Metadata-Version: 2.4
Name: ffvoice
Version: 0.4.7
Summary: High-performance offline speech recognition library for Python
Home-page: https://github.com/chicogong/ffvoice-engine
Author: ffvoice-engine contributors
Author-email: 
License: MIT
Project-URL: Homepage, https://github.com/chicogong/ffvoice-engine
Project-URL: Bug Reports, https://github.com/chicogong/ffvoice-engine/issues
Project-URL: Source, https://github.com/chicogong/ffvoice-engine
Keywords: speech-recognition,asr,whisper,voice-activity-detection,noise-reduction,rnnoise,offline-transcription,real-time-audio
Classifier: Development Status :: 3 - Alpha
Classifier: Intended Audience :: Developers
Classifier: Intended Audience :: Science/Research
Classifier: Topic :: Multimedia :: Sound/Audio :: Speech
